attributes.title: This app is horrible!
attributes.review: I downloaded the app but all that I saw was 20 hour videos of goats screaming! 🐐🐐🐐🐐🐐🐐🐐🐐I thought that this was great at first but then the goats jumped out of my phone!!! 😱😱😱😱One of them called my mother fat and stole my lunch money. 😭The rest of them formed a militia and took over my house. 😥 They said that they had a warrant but I’m not sure if that means they can take my house. 🤷🏼‍♀️The smallest goat told me that I still have to still pay rent. I was able to get my phone back but this was the only app that was still on it. I tried to delete it but it said that if I did then I would get 12 years of bad luck!😠 I couldn’t risk that! My sister also downloaded the app. She didn’t care about the bad luck so she tried to delete it. It spoiled every future book and movie that she will ever watch. 😫 And then she got punched in the face. 😩 PLEASE DONT DOWNLOAD. SAVE YOURSELF. 🧚🏻🌟🧚🏻‍♀️✨Have a good day🧚🏻💫✨🧚🏻‍♂️⚡️
